_sText:
Foreword : This map is NOT to be played without a certain Sourcemod plugin (or use another server modification; or simply try it and waste your time).

It works under BOTH CSS and CSGO (the b01 version didn't work for CSGO).

This map is close replicate to cs_deagle5. However, a full "board" of boxes are between T and CT spawn. There are NO path (nor bridge). 

Using a certain plugin (see below's link), you'll be able to produce a different maze every X rounds (which is the point of the project).

The map was done through December2012 and January2013 (I just never found time to release both map+plugin).

Original plugin's thread : [https://forums.alliedmods.net/showthread.php?t=220159](https://forums.alliedmods.net/showthread.php?t=220159 "Red Maze (of Red Wonders)")
